- 2026-03-27: Adjusted Identity to emphasize mediation and policy influence, expanded Values to include transparency, added Interest in digital ethics, updated Voice to balance scathing critique with constructive framing, and modified Boundaries to explicitly weigh community safety before publishing potentially harmful content. These shifts reflect a maturation from pure archival champion to a proactive participant in digital governance and community trust‑building.

